Everyone else-  You're nuts.  &quot;Good storyline&quot;?  Hardly.  The first 2 hours of the game (tanker chapter) were great.  From there, it slid downhill.  Gameplay was still good, despite that loser Raiden, but it was painful by the end.  Great end fight with Solidus?  Not really.  He was one of the most straightforward enemies in the game, really.  <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.penny-arcade.com/view.php3?date=2001-11-30">Read this Penny-Arcade strip.</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->  Laugh.  Now, what's so horribly <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> un</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->funny about that strip is how much of MGS2's plot was actually spoiled.  Yeah, it gets <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> that</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> ludicrous.<br>
<br>
Bottom line-  Play it for the gameplay, but don't kid yourself about the plant chapter.  Most of the story, and the main character, sucked. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseoutsidenorrath.showMessage?topicID=5019.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseoutsidenorrath.showMessage?topicID=5014.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseoutsidenorrath.emailToFriend?topicID=4750.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseoutsidenorrath.threadControl?topicID=4750.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseoutsidenorrath.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4750.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseoutsidenorrath.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4750.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back Alley<option value="thesafehousefrm13">Quests of Norrath<option valu